<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''乙胺丁醇'''（{{lang-en|Ethambutol}}，簡稱為'''EMB'''或'''E'''）是治療[[結核病|結核病]]的藥物<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web | title = Ethambutol Hydrochloride | url = https://www.drugs.com/monograph/ethambutol-hydrochloride.html | work = drugs.com| publisher= [[The_American_Society_of_Health-System_Pharmacists|The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists]] | access-date = 10 December 2016 | url-status = live | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160605151353/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/ethambutol-hydrochloride.html | archive-date = 5 June 2016 }}</ref>
，通常會與其他{{le|抗結核病藥|tuberculosis medications}}，如[[異煙肼|異煙肼]]、[[利福平|利福平]]及[[吡嗪酰胺|吡嗪酰胺]]等合併使用<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book | title = WHO Model Formulary 2008 | year = 2009 | isbn = 9789241547659 | veditors = Stuart MC, Kouimtzi M, Hill SR | hdl = 10665/44053 | publisher = World Health Organization | hdl-access=free |pages=136, 138, 588, 603 }}</ref>。本品也可以用於治療{{le|鳥型分支桿菌|Mycobacterium avium complex}}（{{lang-en|Mycobacterium avium complex}}）和{{le|堪薩斯分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium kansasii}}（{{lang-en|Mycobacterium kansasii}}）等病原菌感染<ref name=AHFS2016/>。乙胺丁醇由[[口服給藥|口服途徑給藥]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
本品常見的副作用為視力症狀、[[關節痛|關節痛]]、[[噁心|噁心]]、[[頭痛|頭痛]]及疲倦<ref name=AHFS2016/>，其他副作用則有[[肝臟疾病|肝臟疾病]]及[[過敏反應|過敏反應]]<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book| vauthors = Hamilton R |title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia |edition= Deluxe Lab-Coat |year= 2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=48}}</ref>。本品不建議用於{{le|視神經炎|Optic neuritis}}患者、嚴重[[腎功能衰竭|腎臟病]]患者及未滿5歲的幼兒<ref name=WHO2008/>。在[[妊娠|懷孕]]或[[母乳哺育|餵母奶]]期間使用本品，對胎兒或嬰兒尚無已知的危害<ref name=WHO2008/><ref>{{cite web|title=Prescribing medicines in pregnancy database|url=http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm#.U1Yw8Bc3tqw|work= TGA.gov.au| publisher= [[Therapeutic_Goods_Administration|Therapeutic Goods Administration]], Department of Health, Australia |access-date=22 April 2014|date=3 March 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408040902/http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm |archive-date=8 April 2014}}</ref>；不過[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]提出警告，在懷孕期間服用本品，可能會導致嬰兒有視力問題<ref name=AHFS2016/>。本品的藥理機制係為干擾細菌的[[代謝|代謝]]路徑<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- History and culture -->
乙胺丁醇發現於1961年<ref>{{cite book| vauthors = Landau R, Achilladelis B, Scriabine A |title=Pharmaceutical Innovation: Revolutionizing Human Health|date=1999|publisher=Chemical Heritage Foundation|isbn=9780941901215|page=171|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IH4lPs6S1bMC&pg=PA171 |language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220090026/https://books.google.ca/books?id=IH4lPs6S1bMC&pg=PA171| archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>，由[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]表列[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]中<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>，目前可在市面上取得[[通用名藥物|學名藥]]<ref name= Ric2015/>。


